        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 5,
        "Speaker": "妮塔病号服",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "都给后勤部写了四次申请了还不换……哎呦我这骶髂关节，啊哟……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 30,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "她木愣地站在宿舍大厅里，脑海中一片浆糊，也分不清眼前的妮塔到底是在故意装傻还是怎样。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 31,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 9,
        "Speaker": "妮塔",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "总之那俩人不在这儿，你要不换个地方再找找？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 32,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不在这里。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 33,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也没在陶的办公室。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 34,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
